` ``text
stdlib/
├── cursor_rules/              ✅ Directory with underscores
│   ├── api-validation.md      ✅ Markdown file with dashes
│   └── security-headers.md    ✅ Markdown file with dashes
├── github_workflows/          ✅ Directory with underscores
│   └── ci-pipeline.md         ✅ Markdown file with dashes
├── test_fixtures/             ✅ Directory with underscores
│   └── sample-data.md         ✅ Markdown file with dashes
└── contributing-guide.md      ✅ Markdown file with dashes
` ``

### ❌ Incorrect Naming Patterns

` ``text
stdlib/
├── cursor-rules/              ❌ Directory using dashes (should use underscores)
│   ├── api_validation.md      ❌ Markdown file using underscores (should use dashes)
│   └── Security Headers.md    ❌ Spaces and capitalization
├── githubWorkflows/           ❌ CamelCase (should be lowercase with underscores)
│   └── CI Pipeline.md         ❌ Spaces and capitalization
├── test-fixtures/             ❌ Directory using dashes (should use underscores)
│   └── sample_data.md         ❌ Markdown file using underscores (should use dashes)
└── CONTRIBUTING.md            ❌ All caps (should be lowercase)
` ``

### Directory Naming Examples

**✅ Correct:**
- `cursor_rules`
- `github_workflows`
- `test_fixtures`
