**❌ Incorrect:**
- `README.md` (capitalization)
- `contributing_guide.md` (underscores instead of dashes)
- `API Documentation.md` (spaces and capitalization)
- `security.policy.md` (multiple dots before extension)
- `codeOfConduct.md` (CamelCase)

